org.sakaiproject.event.cover

Class NotificationService

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sakaiproject.event.cover.NotificationService
  • Deprecated. 
    Static covers should not be used in favour of injection or lookup via the component manager. This cover will be removed in a later version of the Kernel

    public class NotificationService
extends Object

    NotificationService is a static Cover for the NotificationService; see that interface for usage details.
